    <h1>OrelBuy Privacy Policy</h1>
    
    <p>Welcome to OrelBuy, Sri Lanka's premier online store!</p>
    
    <h2>Collection and Use of Information</h2>
    <p>OrelBuy does not collect any personal information such as name or email address from its users.</p>
    
    <h2>Search Functionality</h2>
    <p>When you use the search functionality on OrelBuy, we display search items along with their prices. We do not track or store any user data related to these searches.</p>
    
    <h2>Shopping Cart</h2>
    <p>When you add items to your shopping cart on OrelBuy, we do not collect or store any personal information about you.</p>
    
    <h2>Total Calculation</h2>
    <p>When you check the total of items in your shopping cart, we perform the calculation based on the prices of the items you added. We do not store any personal information for this purpose.</p>
    
    <h2>Contact Us</h2>
    <p>If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy practices, please contact us at support@orelbuy.com.</p>
